### Get Person by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/mass-assignment/person?id=1
Accept: application/json

### Update Person (Full Entity Update)
PUT http://localhost:5000/mass-assignment/person
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Id": 1,
  "FirstName": "John",
  "LastName": "Doe",
  "IsAdmin": true,
  "SubscriptionId": 2
}

### Update Person Using DTO
PUT http://localhost:5000/mass-assignment/persondto
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "Id": 1,
  "FirstName": "Jane",
  "LastName": "Smith"
}
